    "title": "关于时尚类目商品、商家质量问题管控的公告",
    "followRuleId": "1155331247317323776",
    "content": "<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%;\">尊敬的各位商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%;\">为保障广大消费者的权益，提高平台上鞋靴、服饰内衣、运动户外、珠宝首饰、钟表眼镜、箱包皮具、美妆护肤、母婴（仅童装、童鞋）、鲜花/奢侈品（仅奢侈品）类目商品的质量与信誉度，针对上述类目商品质量表现持续处于尾部的商品和商家实施必要的管控措施，具体管控方式如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%;\">管控周期：双周</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%;\">管控方式：警告、降权、屏蔽（仅商品维度）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%;\">开始时间：2024年11月30日起开始实施</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%;\">具体方案：</span></p>\n<ol style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-top: 0px;\">\n<li style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 14px; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%;\">商品维度</span></li>\n</ol>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 414.05pt; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"552\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 9.05pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 414.05pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 9.05pt;\" colspan=\"3\" width=\"552\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: white;\">商品管控措施（双周）</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 20.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 113.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: solid black 1.0pt; border-bottom: none; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: #D0CECE; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 20.0pt;\" width=\"151\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">管控条件</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 143.0pt; border: none; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: #D0CECE; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 20.0pt;\" width=\"191\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">管控阈值（商品质量指数）</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 158.05pt; border: none; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: #D0CECE; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 20.0pt;\" width=\"211\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">管控措施</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 113.0pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"151\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">商品质量指数C级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 143.0pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; border-left: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"191\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">落入C等级1~6次</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 158.05pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; border-left: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"211\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">预警</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 143.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"191\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">落入C等级累计&ge;7次</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 158.05pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"211\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">降权7天（降权50%）</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 113.0pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" rowspan=\"3\" width=\"151\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">商品质量指数D级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 143.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"191\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">落入D级累计1-3次</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 158.05pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"211\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">预警</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 143.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"191\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">落入D等级累计4-6次</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 158.05pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"211\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">降权7天（降权50%）</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 4.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 143.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 4.5pt;\" width=\"191\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">落入D等级累计&ge;7次</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 158.05pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 4.5pt;\" width=\"211\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">屏蔽7天</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ol style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-top: 0px;\" start=\"2\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 14px; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">商家维度</span></li>\n</ol>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 413.65pt; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"552\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 413.65pt; border-top: none; border-left: solid black 1.0pt; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" colspan=\"3\" width=\"552\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: white;\">商家管控措施（双周）</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 107.1pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; border-top: none; background: #D0CECE; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"143\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">管控条件</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 198.85pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: #D0CECE; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"265\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">管控阈值（店铺+三级类目QCR）</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 107.7pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: #D0CECE; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"144\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">管控措施</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 107.1pt; border-top: none; border-left: solid black 1.0pt; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" rowspan=\"3\" width=\"143\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">双周内完成订单数&ge;20单</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 198.85pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"265\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">均&ge;1.5倍所属三级类目均值</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 107.7pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"144\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">警告</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 198.85pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"265\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">均&ge;2倍所属三级类目均值</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 107.7pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"144\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">降权7天（降权50%）</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 198.85pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"265\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">均&ge;3倍所属三级类目均值</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 107.7pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"144\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">降权14天（降权50%）</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 413.65pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" colspan=\"3\" width=\"552\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: '京东朗正体 玲珑'; color: black;\">管控方式：双周一期统计数据，针对不达标店铺触发预警，6期内累计4期（含）不达标，基于第4期不达标数据进行全店管控。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%;\">各位商家，我们诚邀您与我们共同努力，持续提高商品质量，让消费者在这里购物放心、满意。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">本次调整于2024年11月22日公示通知，将于2024年11月30日正式生效。</span> </span></p>",
